commit_message:
Environment command added

What is done:
* cliff implemented commands for environment control added;
* EnvironmentAction removed from old code base as it is substituded by
  cliff command;
* unit tests for environement command added;
* tests for old commands updated.

Change-Id: Ib0148c48af6f87960735ca10220865661e572095
Implements: blueprint refactoring-for-fuelclient
